ed": "Szczegóły zdarzenia: Zajęcia socjalizacji kotów", "block_type": "atrybut:aria-label", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Event details: Open Doors Day", "translated": "Szczegóły zdarzenia: Dzień otwartych drzwi", "block_type": "atrybut:aria-label", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/event/kitten-adoption-day/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/event/kitten-adoption-day/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/event/cat-socialising-class/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/event/cat-socialising-class/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/event/open-doors-day/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/event/open-doors-day/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.15s\">STARE</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.23s\">—</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.31s\">Spring</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.39s\">Picnic</span></span>", "translated": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">STARE</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">—</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Wiosenna</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Piknik</span></span>", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "This event has already passed — it should not be visible on the front page.", "translated": "To wydarzenie już się odbyło — nie powinno być widoczne na stronie głównej.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Cats&#039;N&#039;Board · Event", "translated": "Cats&#039;N&#039;Board · Wydarzenie", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "STARE", "translated": "STARE", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Spring", "translated": "Wiosenna", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Picnic", "translated": "Piknik", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Tuesday, June 30", "translated": "Wtorek, 30 czerwca", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "10:00 am", "translated": "10:00", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Date", "translated": "Data", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "June 30, 2026", "translated": "30 czerwca 2026", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Time", "translated": "Godzina", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Place", "translated": "Miejsce", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Category", "translated": "Kategoria", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/event/stare-spring-picnic/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/event/stare-spring-picnic/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.15s\">Open</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.23s\">Doors</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.31s\">Day</span></span>", "translated": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Dzień</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Otwartych</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Drzwi</span></span>", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Curious where your cat would stay? Come and see for yourself. Our doors are open all day — walk through the boarding rooms, peek into the sunny nap spots and play areas, and meet the aunties and uncles who'll be looking after your furry friend. Ask us anything: feeding, medication, how we keep shy cats comfortable, how booking works. No appointment needed, bring the whole family. It's the easiest way to know your cat will be in good hands.", "translated": "Ciekaw, gdzie przebywałaby Twoja kota? Przyjdź i przekonaj się osobiście. Nasze drzwi są otwarte przez cały dzień — przejdź przez pokoje pensjonatu, zajrzyj do słonecznych kącików do drzemki i stref zabawy, i poznaj ciocie i wujków, którzy będą opiekować się Twoim futerkowskim przyjacielem. Pytaj nas o wszystko: karmienie, leki, jak dbamy o komfort nieśmiałych kotów, jak działa rezerwacja. Bez konieczności umówienia się, możesz przynieść całą rodzinę. To najłatwiejszy sposób, aby wiedzieć, że Twoja kota będzie w dobrych rękach.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Open", "translated": "Dzień", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Doors", "translated": "Otwartych", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Day", "translated": "Drzwi", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Friday, July 24", "translated": "Piątek, 24 lipca", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "July 24, 2026", "translated": "24 lipca 2026", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.15s\">Cat</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.23s\">Socialising</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.31s\">Class</span></span>", "translated": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Klasa</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Socjalizacji</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Kotów</span></span>", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "A calm, gentle session for shy or nervous cats who need a little help feeling safe around people and other cats. In a quiet space and at your cat's own pace, we use positive play and slow introductions to build confidence — no forcing, no stress. Our carer will guide you through simple techniques you can continue at home. Perfect for kittens finding their paws or older cats who stay hidden when guests arrive. Small group, big patience.", "translated": "Spokojna, łagodna sesja dla nieśmiałych lub zdenerwowanych kotów, którym potrzebna jest trochę pomocy, aby czuć się bezpiecznie wśród ludzi i innych kotów. W spokojnej przestrzeni i w tempie dostosowanym do Twojego kota używamy pozytywnej zabawy i powolnych wprowadzeń, aby budować pewność siebie — bez zmuszania, bez stresu. Nasz opiekun poprowadzi Cię przez proste techniki, które możesz kontynuować w domu. Idealne dla kociąt poznających świat lub starszych kotów, które się ukrywają, gdy przychodzą goście. Mała grupa, duża cierpliwość.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Cat", "translated": "Kot", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Socialising", "translated": "Socjalizacja", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Wednesday, July 15", "translated": "Środa, 15 lipca", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "July 15, 2026", "translated": "15 lipca 2026", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Spots", "translated": "Miejsca", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.15s\">Kitten</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.23s\">Adoption</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\" style=\"animation-delay:0.31s\">Day</span></span>", "translated": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Dzień</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Adopcji</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Kociąt</span></span>", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Spend an afternoon with our kittens who are ready to find their forever homes. You'll get to meet each little one, learn about their personality and needs, and chat with our carers about what adopting a cat really involves. No pressure to decide on the spot — come just to say hello, give some cuddles, and see if one of them purrs their way into your heart. Coffee, treats and plenty of kittens included.", "translated": "Spędź popołudnie z naszymi kociątami, które czekają na znalezienie swojego stałego domu. Będziesz mieć okazję poznać każdego małego towarzysza, dowiedzieć się o ich charakterze i potrzebach, oraz porozmawiać z naszymi opiekunami o tym, co naprawdę wiąże się z adopcją kota. Bez presji, aby zdecydować od razu — przyjdź po prostu pozdrowić je, przymilić się i sprawdzić, czy któreś z nich purrknie sobie do twojego serca. Kawa, przysmaki i mnóstwo kociąt w zestawie.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Kitten", "translated": "Kocię", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Wednesday, July 8", "translated": "Środa, 8 lipca", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "July 8, 2026", "translated": "8 lipca 2026", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Site info", "translated": "Informacje o stronie", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/site-info/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/site-info/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Privacy Policy", "translated": "Polityka Prywatności", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/privacy-policy/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/privacy-policy/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Photo credits", "translated": "Źródła zdjęć", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "href=\"https://example.com/photo-credits/\"", "translated": "href=\"https://example.com/photo-credits/?lang=pl\"", "block_type": "link", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<a href=\"https://example.com/gallery/\" aria-current=\"page\">GALLERY</a>", "translated": "<a href=\"https://example.com/gallery/\">GALERIA</a>", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Our</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">days</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi pnb-akc\">in</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi pnb-akc\">frames.</span></span>", "translated": "<span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">Nasze</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi\">dni</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi pnb-akc\">w</span></span> <span class=\"pnb-wm\"><span class=\"pnb-wi pnb-akc\">kadrach.</span></span>", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "01 — Morning hello", "translated": "01 — Poranek pełen powitań", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "02 — Playtime", "translated": "02 — Czas zabawy", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "03 — Sunbath nap", "translated": "03 — Drzemka na słońcu", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "04 — Bird watching", "translated": "04 — Obserwacja ptaków", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "05 — Lunch o&#039;clock", "translated": "05 — Pora obiadowa", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "06 — Grooming", "translated": "06 — Pielęgnacja", "block_type": "blok:figcaption", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Moments that <em>stay</em>.", "translated": "Chwile, które <em>zostają</em>.", "block_type": "blok:h2", "status": "1"}, {"original": "They look even better <em>in person</em>.", "translated": "Wyglądają jeszcze lepiej <em>osobiście</em>.", "block_type": "blok:h2", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Come say hi — your cat will love it here.", "translated": "Przyjdź powiedzieć cześć — Twój kot będzie tutaj szczęśliwy.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Our", "translated": "Nasze", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "days", "translated": "dni", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "in", "translated": "w", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "frames.", "translated": "kadrach.", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Scroll — photos ride. Click — a frame grows.", "translated": "Przewiń — zdjęcia płyną. Kliknij — kadr się powiększa.", "block_type": "lisc:div", "status": "1"}, {"original": "— keep scrolling —", "translated": "— ciągnij dalej —", "block_type": "lisc:div", "status": "1"}, {"original": "stay", "translated": "zostają", "block_type": "lisc:em", "status": "1"}, {"original": "in person", "translated": "osobiście", "block_type": "lisc:em", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Book a visit →", "translated": "Umów wizytę →", "block_type": "lisc:a", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Close ✕", "translated": "Zamknij ✕", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Our days in frames.", "translated": "Nasze dni w kadrach.", "block_type": "atrybut:aria-label", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Morning hello", "translated": "Poranek pełen powitań", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Playtime", "translated": "Czas zabawy", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Sunbath nap", "translated": "Drzemka na słońcu", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Bird watching", "translated": "Obserwowanie ptaków", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Lunch o&#039;clock", "translated": "Pora lunchu", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Grooming", "translated": "Pielęgnacja", "block_type": "atrybut:alt", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<a href=\"https://example.com/contact/\" aria-current=\"page\">CONTACT</a>", "translated": "<a href=\"https://example.com/contact/\">KONTAKT</a>", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Whether it&#039;s a weekend getaway or full-time care, reach out and we&#039;ll find the purr-fect plan.", "translated": "Niezależnie od tego, czy planujesz weekend poza domem, czy stałą opiekę, skontaktuj się z nami, a my znajdziemy idealny plan.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Say hello", "translated": "Cześć", "block_type": "blok:h2", "status": "1"}, {"original": "We usually reply within a day. Pop in for a tour any time — the kettle (and the treats) are always on.", "translated": "Zwykle odpowiadamy w ciągu dnia. Wpadnij na zwiedzanie kiedykolwiek — czajnik (i smakołyki) zawsze czekają.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Your cat&#039;s name", "translated": "Imię Twojego kota", "block_type": "blok:label", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Message", "translated": "Wiadomość", "block_type": "blok:label", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Send message →", "translated": "Wyślij wiadomość →", "block_type": "blok:button", "status": "1"}, {"original": "This is a demo form — it doesn&#039;t send anything yet. Connect a form plugin (e.g. Contact Form 7 / WPForms) to go live.", "translated": "To formularz demonstracyjny — nic jeszcze nie wysyła. Połącz wtyczkę formularza (np. Contact Form 7 / WPForms), aby uruchomić funkcję.", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Tell us a little about your cat and the dates you have in mind…", "translated": "Opowiedz nam nieco o swoim kocie i terminy, które masz na myśli…", "block_type": "atrybut:placeholder", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<a href=\"https://example.com/our-location/\" aria-current=\"page\">OUR FACILITIES</a>", "translated": "<a href=\"https://example.com/our-location/\">NASZE OBIEKTY</a>", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Our facilities", "translated": "Nasze obiekty", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Sunny rooms, cosy nooks and plenty of window sills — a calm holiday home in the heart of Żoliborz.", "translated": "Słoneczne pokoje, przytulne kąty i wiele parapetów — spokojny dom wakacyjny w sercu Żoliborza.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Our location", "translated": "Nasza lokalizacja", "block_type": "blok:h2", "status": "1"}, {"original": "You&#039;ll find us on a quiet street in the heart of Żoliborz — sunny rooms, cosy nooks and plenty of window sills for sunbathing.", "translated": "Znajdziesz nas na spokojnej ulicy w sercu Żoliborza — słoneczne pokoje, przytulne kąty i wiele parapetów do opalania się.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Drop by for a tour, meet the team and let your cat sniff out its new holiday home.", "translated": "Wpadnij na zwiedzanie, poznaj zespół i pozwól swojemu kotowi obwąchać nowy dom wakacyjny.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Come and visit", "translated": "Odwiedź nas", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "<a href=\"https://example.com/our-staff/\" aria-current=\"page\">OUR TEAM</a>", "translated": "<a href=\"https://example.com/our-staff/\">NASZ ZESPÓŁ</a>", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Best Animal Aunties &amp; Uncles", "translated": "Najlepsze Ciocie i Wujkowie Zwierząt", "block_type": "blok:h1", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Calm, patient and genuinely cat-obsessed — meet the team who will look after your companion like their own.", "translated": "Spokojni, cierpliwi i naprawdę zakochani w kotach — poznaj zespół, który zaopiekuje się Twoim pupilem jak swoim własnym.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "The people your cat will love", "translated": "Ludzie, których pokochamy Twojego kota", "block_type": "lisc:span", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Ola", "translated": "Ola", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Tomek", "translated": "Tomek", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Kasia", "translated": "Kasia", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Marek", "translated": "Marek", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Ania", "translated": "Ania", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Bartek", "translated": "Bartek", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Julia", "translated": "Julia", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Paweł", "translated": "Paweł", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Magda", "translated": "Magda", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Filip", "translated": "Filip", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Natalia", "translated": "Natalia", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Zosia", "translated": "Zosia", "block_type": "lisc:b", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Transparent rates with no surprises. Longer stays and multiple cats get a friendly discount — just ask.", "translated": "Przejrzyste stawki bez niespodzianek. Dłuższe pobyty i wiele kotów otrzymują przyjazny rabat &#8211; wystarczy zapytać.", "block_type": "blok:p", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Supervised play &amp; rest", "translated": "Nadzorowana zabawa i odpoczynek", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Fresh food &amp; water", "translated": "Świeża woda i jedzenie", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Sunny window spots", "translated": "Słoneczne parapety", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Daily photo update", "translated": "Codzienna aktualizacja zdjęcia", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Cosy private room", "translated": "Przytulny prywatny pokój", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Two play sessions daily", "translated": "Dwie sesje zabawy dziennie", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Litter &amp; grooming care", "translated": "Opieka nad kuwetą i pielęgnacja", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Photo &amp; message updates", "translated": "Aktualizacje zdjęć i wiadomości", "block_type": "blok:li", "status": "1"}, {"original": "Care in your own home", "translated":